{
  "stem": "5356.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we sat down to eat and sing, you know, Zemirot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] That's how we spent, you know, a Saturday-- relaxing, nobody worked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sure, there were certain people in the city but they-- didn't observe-- especially the young at the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember the Socialist movement, the Communist movement in the-- in the '30s.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a-- it was a cultural city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had a Hebrew school, a Tarbut.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had a Mizrachi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went to the Mizrachi school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had a Talmud Torah, and we had a yeshivah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had a bibliotek and we had this artists.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had shows performed by locals or, also, came in troops from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know Morrie Schwartz-- I remember when they played the-- the play, it called [INAUDIBLE] and other plays.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was very cultural, a very nice city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had nice places to go on the summer-- like behind the cemetary, the Christian cemetery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was a hilly place and the water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Or it was on the other side of town, going towards-- from the Jewish cemetery back, was also a river, Opatowska, named after the city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we used to, you know, have places where we could dip in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, the water wasn't that deep that you were afraid you would drown.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had bridges, you know, that connected through those rivers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had a big factory-- Mandelbaum's factory-- to produce soap.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And another factory, which, from all the-- the things that the farmers brought in that made oil.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And otherwise, most of the people were small-- you know, with their small, little business, little stores.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were workers, like tailors, which they-- they made their ware in the-- once a week was the market in our town.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
